## Step Five: Planning Your Wedding Morning Timeline

One of the most common mistakes brides make is **underestimating how long hair and makeup actually takes** — especially for larger wedding parties.

Here's a general guide for timing:

| Service | Estimated Time |
|---|---|
| Bridal Makeup | 75–90 minutes |
| Bridesmaid Makeup | 45–60 minutes per person |
| Mother of Bride/Groom Makeup | 45–60 minutes per person |
| Bridal Hair | 60–90 minutes |
| Bridesmaid Hair | 45–60 minutes per person |

**Always build in buffer time.** Someone will be late. Someone will need a touch-up